Sketch the region. $xz$-plane is $y=0$. $yz$-plane is $x=0$. $xy$-plane is $z=0$. So the region is bounded by $0\leq x\leq 1$, $0\leq y\leq 1$ and $0\leq z\leq 2x^2+9y^4$. It is shown below.
